descript.abstract: This data set shows the locations of local parks, excluding State and Federaly owned parks.
descript.purpose: The data was developed for the State Geogrphic Information Database (SGID). State and Federal parks can be located in the SGID in the dataset CADASTRE.LandOwnership.
